interpretation: The "printer" card represents the manifestation of ideas and communication. It signifies the ability to bring thoughts and concepts into tangible form, whether that be through physical printing or other means of expression. This card encourages the seeker to trust their own creative process and to bring their ideas into the world with confidence. It can also suggest the need for organization and attention to detail in order to effectively communicate one's message. Keywords associated with this card include productivity, communication, expression, creation, and manifestation.
